OL,3,CCalls for action after fatal
OL,4,Celectrocution of runner
OL,6,FA coroner has called on energy network
OL,7,Foperators to make their infrastructure
OL,8,Fsafer to prevent future deaths.
OL,10,FIt comes after a runner was fatally
OL,11,Felectrocuted whilst running in the
OL,12,FLake District.
OL,14,FJohn Henry Oates, known as Harry, was
OL,15,Ffound dead on October 27 2023, in the
OL,16,Farea of Lupton, near Kendal. An
OL,17,Finquest into his death found he was
OL,18,Fkilled instantly when he came into
OL,19,Fcontact with a low-hanging electricity
OL,20,Fcable whilst on a run.
