OL,3,CCalls for action after fatal
OL,4,Celectrocution of runner
OL,6,FKirsty Gomersal, the senior coroner
OL,7,Ffor Cumbria, has now written a Report
OL,8,Fto Prevent Future Deaths addressed to
OL,9,Fthe Electricity Networks Association
OL,10,F(ENA), calling for action to avoid a
OL,11,Frepeat of the incident.
OL,13,FThe coroner concluded in Mr Oates'
OL,14,Finquest that a "rare and complex
OL,15,Fsequence of events" led to his death,
OL,16,Fand said that, in her opinion, there
OL,17,Fis a low "risk that future deaths will
OL,18,Foccur unless action is taken".
OL,20,F'Not experienced before'
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
