OL,6,FThe inquest into Mr Oates' death heard
OL,7,Fthat a 11kv conductor wire was hanging
OL,8,Flow and continued to be live as it did
OL,9,Fnot touch earth.
OL,11,FThe coroner was told this was a result
OL,12,Fof the failure of two porcelain
OL,13,Ftension disc insulators, due to voids
OL,14,Fin their concrete filling, which an
OL,15,Finvestigation found was "introduced in
OL,16,Fthe manufacturing process."
OL,18,FThe inquest heard how this double
OL,19,Finsulator failure "had not been known
OL,20,Fto previously occur."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
