OL,4,Celectrocution of runner
OL,6,FThe fault on the electricity pole was
OL,7,Frecorded at the time as a "phase to
OL,8,Fphase" fault, which, before Mr Oates'
OL,9,Fdeath, "was not known to lead to a low-
OL,10,Fhanging line."
OL,12,FSince the incident, Electricity North
OL,13,FWest (ENWL), who is responsible for
OL,14,Fthe electrical infrastructure in
OL,15,Fquestion, has stopped using porcelain
OL,16,Finsulators - which had been employed
OL,17,Fby the industry since the 1950s.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
