OL,3,CCalls for action after fatal
OL,4,Celectrocution of runner
OL,6,FIt says it will work to replace the
OL,7,Fremaining insulators of this kind when
OL,8,Fmaintenance work is required. There
OL,9,Fare around 8,000 locations within the
OL,10,FENWL network where porcelain
OL,11,Finsulators are present.
OL,13,F'Safety the highest priority'
OL,15,FIn response to coroner Gomersal's
OL,16,Freport, a spokesperson for Energy
OL,17,FNetworks Association said: "Our
OL,18,Fthoughts are with Mr Oates' loved ones
OL,19,Ffollowing this tragic event.
